    Page: 269
  Source:
    Title: The Bhagavad Gita
  Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
---
Let your mind be filled with Me,
and become devoted to Me.
Untie your heart with Mine.
See Me as the ultimate Goal.
Filled with Me, you will come to Me.
